OL,3,CScottish government announces national
OL,4,Creview into grooming gangs
OL,6,FOn hearing the news, one victim told
OL,7,FITV News it could help others come
OL,8,Fforward, as ITV News Scotland
OL,9,FCorrespondent Peter Smith reports
OL,11,FWords by ITV News Scotland
OL,12,FCorrespondent Peter Smith and Scotland
OL,13,FProducer Stephanie Docherty
OL,15,FThe Scottish government has announced
OL,16,Fan independent national review of
OL,17,Fgroup-based child sexual abuse and
OL,18,Fexploitation, which, they say, will
OL,19,Fhelp them decide on whether a public
OL,20,Finquiry is necessary.
