OL,6,FScotland's first minister and justice
OL,7,Fsecretary have been under continued
OL,8,Fpressure to launch such an inquiry,
OL,9,Fsimilar to the grooming inquiry
OL,10,Fongoing in England, as more victims in
OL,11,FScotland come forward.
OL,13,FLast week, ITV News spoke to 'Taylor',
OL,14,Fwho told us that she was sexually
OL,15,Fabused by a group of Pakistani men
OL,16,Fwhile growing up in the care system in
OL,17,Fthe West of Scotland.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
