OL,6,FShe was calling for the Scottish
OL,7,Fgovernment to acknowledge the
OL,8,Fexistence of grooming gangs and launch
OL,9,Fa review.
OL,11,FAfter hearing her story, two more
OL,12,Fwomen have come forward saying they
OL,13,Fwere also preyed upon and abused by
OL,14,Fgroups of men while they were young
OL,15,Fgirls in the care system in Glasgow.
OL,17,FWe are calling them Amy and Sarah.
OL,19,FAmy says she was first approached by
OL,20,Fthe gang when she was aged 12 in
OL,21,FGlasgow's Central Station.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
