OL,6,FSarah said: "They were giving me the
OL,7,Fgifts, the attention, the money, the
OL,8,Fnew clothes - in care, nobody else was
OL,9,Fgiving me that kind of affection."
OL,11,FBut the women say quite quickly the
OL,12,Fmen wanted something in return, and
OL,13,Fthey were regularly taken to flats,
OL,14,Fhotel rooms and parties and told to
OL,15,Fhave sex with groups of men.
OL,17,FPreviously, the Scottish government
OL,18,Fsaid there was not enough evidence to
OL,19,Fjustify such an inquiry in Scotland.
