OL,6,FSarah and Amy welcomed the change of
OL,7,Fposition and announcement of an
OL,8,Findependent review.
OL,10,F"This might mean other people come
OL,11,Fforward. That they will believe they
OL,12,Fare being heard," said Sarah.
OL,14,FAmy added: "That's exactly what it is
OL,15,Fabout for me, that I am being heard.
OL,16,FI'm not worthless, no, I'm not dirty,
OL,17,Fno, I'm not damaged goods. I was
OL,18,Fgroomed, I was a child, I was 12.
OL,19,FPeople were supposed to protect me."
