OL,6,FFor many, a review falls short of a
OL,7,Fpublic inquiry, but it is one step
OL,8,Fcloser to getting answers for those
OL,9,Fwho were abused and accountability for
OL,10,Fthose who failed them.
OL,12,FEducation Secretary Jenny Gilruth
OL,13,Fsaid: "Our thoughts are with victims
OL,14,Fof child abuse who have already
OL,15,Fsuffered so much ` this matter must be
OL,16,Fhandled sensitively and with the
OL,17,Futmost respect and consideration for
OL,18,Ftheir experiences.
