OL,6,F"The issue of group-based sexual abuse
OL,7,Fand exploitation of children is
OL,8,Fsensitive and complex, and the
OL,9,FScottish Government has been giving it
OL,10,Fvery detailed consideration. We have
OL,11,Fbeen clear that we are prepared to
OL,12,Fgive every consideration to an inquiry
OL,13,Fon this issue, and that any such
OL,14,Fdecision needs to be based on
OL,15,Finformation, evidence and a greater
OL,16,Funderstanding of the scale and nature
OL,17,Fof this form of abuse and of the
OL,18,Fresponses to it."
