OL,6,FProfessor Alexis Jay, who chaired the
OL,7,FIndependent Inquiry into Child Sexual
OL,8,FAbuse in England and Wales and has
OL,9,Fongoing work on Scotland's national
OL,10,Fchild sexual abuse and exploitation
OL,11,Fstrategic group, will lead the review.
OL,13,FShe is set to meet with Police
OL,14,FScotland in the new year.
OL,16,FProfessor Alexis Jay said: "I am
OL,17,Fpleased to take on the role of Chair
OL,18,Fof the National Group, and to build on
OL,19,Fthe excellent leadership of my
OL,20,Fpredecessors, Iona Colvin and Sarah
OL,21,FTaylor.
